# Phase 1: Analyze the Fix

This is a patch for AggressiveInstCombine:

[AggressiveInstCombine] POPCNT generation for bit-count pattern
The proposal is to enhance LLVM by teaching it to recognize the pattern and replace it with the hardware POPCNT instruction.
